@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080

### Health
GET {{baseUrl}}/health

### DB time
GET {{baseUrl}}/db-time

### Sync stocks from external API
POST {{baseUrl}}/stocks/sync?limit=10

### Sync stocks from external API (JSON body)
POST {{baseUrl}}/stocks/sync
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "limit": 10
}

### List stocks
GET {{baseUrl}}/stocks?limit=20&offset=0&sort_by=ticker&order=asc

### Search stocks
GET {{baseUrl}}/stocks?q=apple&action=buy&limit=20&offset=0

### Stock detail
GET {{baseUrl}}/stocks/AAPL

### Recommendations
GET {{baseUrl}}/stocks/recommendations?limit=5

### Swagger OpenAPI JSON
GET {{baseUrl}}/swagger/doc.json
